Florence Namayanja (amụrụ n'ụbọchị nke anọ n'ọnwa Ọktoba n'afọ 1960) bụ nwanyị ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị Ugandan bụ onye nnọchi anya nwanyị distrikti nke Bukoto County East, Masaka District. Ọ nọ n'òtù ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị Democratic Party ma ugbu a ọ nọ na National Unity Platform. Na Nzukọ Ndị Omeiwu nke iri na otu, ọ guzoro dị ka onye na-azọ ọkwa onye isi oche LC5 maka Masaka City n'okpuru National Unity Platform ọ bụ ezie na ọ meriri na ntuli aka ahụ. Ọ bụ onye mmeri nke oche onye isi obodo Masaka mgbe o meriri mmadụ asaa gụnyere onye ọchụnta ego, Emmanuel Lwasa na vootu 28,824.
A mụrụ Namayanja na John Kisomose Mukasa na Pirajiya Namatove nwụrụ anwụ ma ọ bụ nke ise a mụrụ n'ezinụlọ nwere ụmụ asatọ. N'afọ 1978, ọ nwetara asambodo agụmakwụkwọ Uganda ya na Masaka S.S.S

ma mgbe ọ sonyeere Makerere Day na Evening Classes for Adults maka asambodo agụmụbe Uganda Advanced ya ma mechaa ya n'afọ 2003. O nwere asambodo na Human Resource Management na Gọọmentị Obodo (2004) na asambodo na Leadership na Management (2005) site na Uganda Management Institute.  N'afọ 2007, ọ sonyeere Mahadum Makerere maka nzere bachelọ ya na Industrial and Organizational Psychology. N'otu afọ ahụ (2007), e nyere ya asambodo na Building Communities of Character site na Character Training Institute, Oklahoma.
Ọ bụ onye nchịkwa na National Water and Sew.Corp (1981-1994)

O mechara were ya n'ọrụ dị ka onye otu Council na Mulago School of Nursing (2008-2009) na Kyambogo University Council (2006-2011). N'otu afọ ahụ (2006-2011), ọ rụrụ ọrụ dị ka onye otu Board na National Water & Sewerage Corporation
Tụkwasị na nke a, ọ bụ onye ndụmọdụ LC5 (2001-2006) na osote onye isi obodo Kampala City (2006-2011).

Site n'afọ 2011 ruo n'afọ 2016, ọ bụ onye omeiwu nke Uganda na omeiwu nke Ukraine na nke itoolu na nke iri. Ọ rụrụ ọrụ ọzọ na Nzukọ Ndị Omeiwu nke Uganda na Kọmitii na-ahụ maka ihe onwunwe, na Kọmiti na Kọmisi, Ndị Ọchịchị Steeti na Ụlọ Ọrụ Steeti.
Ihe ntụrụndụ ya bụ ịchọpụta ihe ọhụrụ, na ime ndị enyi ọhụrụ
Ọ bụ onye Rotarian na onye ndú ụmụ nwanyị (Onye isi nke DP Women League).

E jidere Florence Namayanja na Dr Abed Bwanika, onye National Unity Platform- NUP na-azọ ọkwa onye isi ala n'oge ngagharị iwe ndị sochiri njide Robert Kyagulanyi Ssentamu.  E jidere ha na Evan K Gameu, onye na-azọ ọkwa onye omeiwu nke Bukoto East NUP na Juliet Kakande Nakabuye, onye na na-azọrọ ọkwa onye omebe iwu nke Masaka ma boo ha ebubo ịkpali ime ihe ike na ime ihe nwere ike ịgbasa ọrịa na-efe efe, n'okpuru ngalaba 171 nke Iwu Iwu Iwu. E mechara tọhapụ ha na mgbapụta.
